title: GetPropertyReferenceCount (Method)
text:
METHOD GetPropertyReferenceCount : CmpBACnet.IEC_BACNET_STATUS
Gets the number of device object property reference entries in the List_Of_Object_Property_References-Property of this BACnet-Object.

rows.Name: count
rows.Comment:
The number of property references of the
List_Of_Object_Property_References of this object.
